id = "003 - tithe"
title = "Tithe"
description = "Word travels fast when coin changes hands. The Realm wants its cut... a tithe, they call it. Fair enough, every market has a toll. But I'd better make sure I'm earning faster than they're taking, or this venture dries up quick. "
